name: Austin Bronco - The Crazy Gunslinging Cowboy Shooter
name_original: Austin Bronco - The Crazy Gunslinging Cowboy Shooter
description:
Austin Bronco is out to earn as much cash as he can by shooting anyone in sight

Fight through the oncoming enemies and defeat them to steal their cash

Be careful though as Austin will lose if he kills an unarmed man

Sounds straight forward and easy enough to grab a top spot on the leaderboard ?

Funky music and sweet graphics , download now and enjoy the simplistic gameplay

** Sounds by freesfx.co.uk **
